{"type":"message","id":"7920c395","parentId":"fcc4c6fb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:29:33.321Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:8ecc8a2f-8c0c-47da-b813-78ecc92e2cd5 每日新闻与市场早报] 执行每日新闻与市场早报任务：\n0. 查询西安今日天气，生成天气简报，重点给出穿衣建议，提醒是否需要带伞\n\n1. 国际新闻TOP5：搜索\"国际新闻\"、\"世界新闻\"、\"global news\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n2. 国内新闻TOP5：搜索\"国内新闻\"、\"中国新闻\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n3. 半导体行业新闻：搜索\"半导体行业新闻\"、\"WiFi芯片\"、\"芯片验证\"、\"ESP32\"、\"乐鑫\"，输出10条行业新闻摘要\n\n4. 乐鑫科技(688018)股票分析：获取最新股价、涨跌幅、成交量，搜索公司公告、研报、最新消息，给出持有/卖出的建议\n\n5. 股票推荐TOP5：搜索\"股票推荐\"、\"买入评级\"、\"券商推荐股票\"，推荐10个值得关注的股票及理由\n\n6. 基金推荐TOP5：搜索\"基金推荐\"、\"优质基金\"、\"基金排行\"，推荐10个值得买入的基金及理由\n\n7. openclaw，claude code及其同类产品的最新进展\n\n输出要求：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 同时将所有信息整理成一个飞书文档，将飞书文档链接附在飞书卡片最后\n- 每个部分用清晰标题分隔\n- 重要信息加粗\n- 股票/基金推荐包含代码/名称+推荐理由\n- 每条新闻/信息必须附上来源和链接，格式：📰 [新闻标题] - [一句话摘要]\\n🔗 来源：[网站名称] | [链接]\n- 如果某条信息无法找到确切来源，标注\"来源待确认\"\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 09:29 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-30 01:29 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774834173318}}
{"type":"message","id":"f64b18f8","parentId":"7920c395","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:29:52.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个cron任务，要求生成每日新闻与市场早报。任务内容很多，需要：\n\n1. 查询西安天气\n2. 国际新闻TOP5\n3. 国内新闻TOP5\n4. 半导体行业新闻\n5. 乐鑫科技股票分析\n6. 股票推荐TOP5\n7. 基金推荐TOP5\n8. openclaw/claude code等产品的最新进展\n\n输出要求：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 创建飞书文档并在卡片中附上链接\n- 每条信息需要来源和链接\n- 完成后发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\n\n让我先读取weather skill来了解如何获取天气信息，然后开始执行任务。\n\n首先，我需要：\n1. 查询天气\n2. 搜索各种新闻和信息\n3. 创建飞书文档\n4. 发送飞书卡片\n\n让我开始执行。首先读取weather skill。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我将为您执行每日新闻与市场早报任务。让我先读取天气skill，然后开始收集信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_733eb37be4c74c9b995764a1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\skills\\weather\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":22983,"output":493,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23476,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774834173321,"responseId":"e4789543c561e0fb4b5a03a46ce70d79"}}
{"type":"message","id":"13fcef6f","parentId":"f64b18f8","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:29:52.929Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_733eb37be4c74c9b995764a1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"☔\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"curl\",\n              \"bins\": [\"curl\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install curl (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774834192928}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb689700","parentId":"13fcef6f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:30:05.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在知道如何获取天气了。让我开始执行任务。我需要同时进行多个搜索来收集信息。让我开始：\n\n1. 先获取西安天气\n2. 搜索国际新闻\n3. 搜索国内新闻\n4. 搜索半导体行业新闻\n5. 搜索乐鑫科技股票信息\n6. 搜索股票推荐\n7. 搜索基金推荐\n8. 搜索openclaw/claude code最新进展\n\n让我并行执行这些搜索任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_17529bac250546f2a9fbc3b5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"wttr.in/Xi'an?format=v2\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c36c280b401f4041925b801e","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"国际新闻 global news world news 今日","count":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_26b11d97740f4aff99a93c89","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"国内新闻 中国新闻 今日","count":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_80fa4bc422b64bc2963a6b15","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"半导体行业新闻 WiFi芯片 芯片验证 ESP32 乐鑫","count":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f43265b386814d2bb9f9abde","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"乐鑫科技 688018 股价 最新消息 公告 研报","count":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aef6fd288ddf4dd883d9d76e","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"股票推荐 买入评级 券商推荐 2026","count":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14d9d1e2e9c148b9956eb574","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"基金推荐 优质基金 基金排行 2026","count":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_942443cba0e2425681e36100","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"openclaw claude code cursor windsurf AI coding assistant 2026","count":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":23981,"output":418,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774834192929,"responseId":"ad52bedf36ce5432a25ae2c9f5551d17"}}
